## Two Interfaces
 
This project ships with two Streamlit dashboards:
 
### 🌿 app.py — Personal Wellness Monitor (User-Friendly)
Designed for non-technical users. Select sliders describe body feelings in plain language ("Sweaty", "Normal", "Chilly"). The model maps these to quantile-transformed feature vectors and returns a predicted state with a confidence gauge.
 
### 📊 app2.py — Research Dashboard (Technical)
Designed for researchers and clinicians. Numeric sliders represent delta values from a subject's physiological baseline. Includes feature importance visualization, model architecture details, and methodology summary.
 
